    *   **Maximum Accrual:** The maximum amount of PTO an employee can accrue is 15 days per year.
    *   **Carryover:** Employees can carry over a maximum of 5 days of unused PTO from one year to the next. Any PTO exceeding this limit is forfeited.
    *   **Requesting PTO:** PTO requests must be submitted through the NovaAI HR system (Workday) at least two weeks in advance of the requested time off.
    *   **Approval:** PTO requests are subject to manager approval based on business needs and team coverage.
    *   **Payout:** Unused PTO is not paid out upon termination of employment.
    *   **Eligibility:** All full-time and part-time employees are eligible for PTO.
    *   **Policy Document:** The complete PTO policy document can be found on the NovaAI intranet at [link to internal policy document - *This is a placeholder, please replace with the actual link*].
    
