[14:33:22.255] [INFO ]     NovaLens currently supports the following data connectors:
    
    *   **Google Analytics:** Connects to Google Analytics accounts to track website traffic and user behavior.
    *   **Mixpanel:** Integrates with Mixpanel for event tracking and user engagement analysis.
    *   **Amplitude:** Connects to Amplitude for product analytics and user behavior insights.
    *   **Snowflake:** Supports direct connections to Snowflake data warehouses.
    *   **PostgreSQL:** Allows connections to PostgreSQL databases.
    *   **MySQL:** Supports connections to MySQL databases.
    *   **MongoDB:** Connects to MongoDB databases.
    *   **Salesforce:** Integrates with Salesforce for CRM data.
    *   **Looker:** Connects to Looker for data visualization and reporting.
    *   **Tableau:** Connects to Tableau for data visualization and reporting.
    
    Please note that NovaLens is continuously adding new connectors, so this list may be updated in the future. You can find the most up-to-date list on the NovaLens documentation page: [https://novalens.com/docs/connectors](https://novalens.com/docs/connectors)
